+            # Pre-quantized BitNet checkpoints (quantization_config.quant_method
+            # == "bitnet", e.g. microsoft/bitnet-b1.58-2B-4T) are already
+            # dequantized to ternary * (1/weight_scale) by dequant_bitnet() at
+            # load time; re-running weight_quant() here would collapse every
